1. *Odvela* sam psa u park juče. (I took the dog to the park yesterday.)
2. Ona me je *odvela* u bioskop da pogledamo novi film. (She took me to the cinema to watch the new movie.)
3. Kada sam se probudila, shvatila sam da me je neko *odveo* kući. (When I woke up, I realized that someone took me home.)
4. Policija je *odvela* osumnjičenog u pritvor. (The police took the suspect into custody.)
5. Njegova žena ga je *odvela* kod lekara zbog jakih bolova u stomaku. (His wife took him to the doctor because of severe stomach pains.)
6. Učiteljica je *odvela* decu na izlet u prirodu. (The teacher took the children on a field trip to nature.)
7. Sinoć sam videla kako je policija *odvela* neke momke koji su se tučili na ulici. (Last night I saw the police take away some guys who were fighting on the street.)
8. Komšija mi je *odveo* auto u servis da ga poprave. (My neighbor took my car to the mechanic to get it fixed.)
9. Otišla sam u prodavnicu, a moj muž me je *odveo* na večeru u restoran. (I went to the store, and my husband took me out to dinner at a restaurant.)
10. Kada su ga *odveli* u bolnicu, već je bilo prekasno da se spasi njegov život. (When they took him to the hospital, it was already too late to save his life.)